  "text": "The full-wave analysis of the proposed design has been carried out using CST Microwave Studio, utilizing * Correspondence: asondas@kocaeli.edu.tr the time-domain finite-integration technique. In this paper, the simulated antenna performance (S 11 , radiation pattern, electric field distribution, and SAR) is presented. Note that this paper is an extended version of [CITATION_1] , which was previously presented at the ICECCO'2013 conference.",
